"[section anchor]" instead of just "[anchor]" for more context

VERY IMPORTANT: instead of making catalogs using directories, make them using tags that will be inside articles. Catalogs themselves will have tags. Something like:

<catalog>
    <name>Topic name</name>
    <tags>
        <tag>main page item</tag>
    </tags>
    <filters>
        <tags>
            <tag>topic name</tag>
        </tags>
    </filters>
</catalog>

<article>
    <tags>
        <tag>topic name</tag>
    </tags>
    <name>Some article</name>
    <contents>
        <paragraph>This article will be displayed in a "Topic name" catalog!</paragraph>
    </contents>
</article>
